\caption{\textsf{{\footnotesize 2-loop diagrams contributing to the third order of $S$.  Striped double lines correspond to ghost propagators. Note that we does not compute unoriented diagram but modify the result for Hermitean matrix model with even function tree level superpotential.}}}
